<h2> Download Rasmol</h2>
</center>
 Rasmol is an old molecular viewing program that is no longer a supported
product.&nbsp; However,&nbsp; both the Mac and PC versions still work.&nbsp;
The Mac version is a stuffit file and the PC version is a zipped file. 
<p><a href="http://www.uwosh.edu/faculty_staff/gutow/RasMac.sit">Download 
the Macintosh version.</a> </p>
<p><a href="http://www.uwosh.edu/faculty_staff/gutow/RasWin.zip">Download 
the PC/Windows version.</a> </p>
  
